Package dreisoft.tresos.launcher2.api.project Description

This package provides access to the EB tresos projects in the current workspace. Only tresos specific information can be accessed via this interface.

Module Configurations

The class ModuleConfiguration allows to access the module configurations of an ECU Configuration project. The ModuleConfiguration is derrived from ModuleDescription so also the information from the module extension-point can be queried.
